videos.headline: Rosen finds Pabico for TD
videos.description: Josh Rosen connects with Christian Pabico for a 31-yard touchdown to pad UCLA's lead over Oregon.

videos.headline: Oregon TD chips away at UCLA's lead
videos.description: QB Braxton Burmeister rushes from 7 yards out for a touchdown to get Oregon on the board.

videos.headline: Oregon's Burmeister rushes for second TD of the quarter
videos.description: Braxton Burmeister rushes four yards for his second touchdown of the second quarter to tie Oregon's matchup with UCLA right before halftime.

videos.headline: Rosen finds Andrews for TD
videos.description: Josh Rosen connects with an open Darren Andrews for 1-yard touchdown to increase UCLA's lead over Oregon.
